- Add entries to the "## modifications" section when making changes
- Use ✨ for new features
- Use 🐛 for bug fixes
- Use 📊 for test-related changes
- Use 📚 for documentation changes
- Use 📈 for data changes
- Include date in YYYY-MM-DD format
- Add entries in chronological order (newest at top)
- Be specific but concise in descriptions
- Group related changes together
- Always use bash to get the datetime before writing to history: `date +%Y-%m-%d`
